Features of Q-A-OLLAMA-RAG-DOC
=============================

1. **Context-Aware Question Answering**:
   The system uses Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) to answer queries by first retrieving the most relevant documents and then generating accurate responses.

2. **Customizable Document Collection**:
   Users can customize the knowledge base by adding various document types such as text files, PDFs, etc.

3. **Pre-trained NLP Models**:
   The app uses cutting-edge NLP models for both retrieval and generation tasks, ensuring high-quality results.

4. **User-Friendly Interface**:
   The application has a clean and easy-to-use interface for both developers and non-developers to interact with.

5. **Extensible & Scalable**:
   The code is modular and designed to be scalable, making it easy to extend for larger datasets or integrate with other services.
